{"tid":455582,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風追擊】1723號熱帶氣旋 達維 DAMREY  (28W)","createTime":"2017-11-02T08:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T18:41:09.000Z","uid":48733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a6e5af007126abbcd134c3120afde9829321d8d4","tid":455582,"uid":48733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><img src=\"http://imgur.com/Pskei0w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FPskei0w.png&h=13bd482a&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>颱風追擊：熱帶氣旋 達維</ins></span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1723號熱帶氣旋 達維 DAMREY (28W)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">來源：柬埔寨<br />\n意義：象 </span></span></strong> <br />\n【註】 發出颱風追擊帖，表示有熱帶氣旋在南海或西北太平洋一帶形成。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要張貼未經證實的風暴消息、使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新，直至熱帶氣旋消散。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">氣象台專頁現已登場</span> <br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/phDMEEd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FphDMEEd.png&h=c68c509c&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=Od93XWp5wLOUKSfcqLyypE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=9eb43614\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a> <br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/OSjok6Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FOSjok6Z.png&h=fc73419e&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=Od93XWp5wLOUKSfcqLyypE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=8a86cc8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BZfpfrS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h