rmal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要去越南芽莊市（大機會係login password但應該少人去旅行公幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）或者胡志明市（越南最大城市，login後應該近距離北掠影響到，比較多人去旅行公幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）在內既越南南部既，請移玉到下post詢問關於航空交通安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[ATC]熱帶氣旋與航空交通集中討論區</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/395625\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/395625</a><br />\n<br />\n柬埔寨（應該無人要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />） 及泰國首都曼谷一帶（應該最多人問呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）亦可能受達維殘餘雨帶影響但應該唔影響航班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">btw變左洗板金剛棒</span></span>"},{"pid":"b5dda4d076a1fedfe068b680b267d4f6ca17997b","tid":455582,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T09:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca6f1d04cd815ee2b627ddde3d7378ac8e5ebe4","tid":455582,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T09:49:42.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22010b6f28fd05261b45b1c89fe187b7b59f010","tid":455582,"uid":41177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T10:29:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2743d977ef9f38cf897dec84d720d6e7ef14645f","tid":455582,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:01:01.000Z","msg":"市區今晚係熱左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37950f78ed2fef6271d91933344ff9a1f50c21d0","tid":455582,"uid"